690
01:01:54,840 --> 01:01:57,841
I doubt it. I hate artichokes.

691
01:01:58,886 --> 01:01:59,917
You shouldn't.

692
01:01:59,970 --> 01:02:02,046
Watch this.

693
01:02:08,019 --> 01:02:10,095
Take it.

694
01:02:12,233 --> 01:02:14,024
That's better.

695
01:02:27,164 --> 01:02:29,121
Lucien, you're a wizard!

696
01:02:29,166 --> 01:02:31,739
All courtesy of Mr. Collignon.

697
01:02:34,547 --> 01:02:37,583
Mr. Collignon? Lucien...

698
01:02:37,633 --> 01:02:40,420
Sorry, Mr. Dufayel. It just slipped out.

699
01:02:40,469 --> 01:02:42,627
Practice, Lucien!

700
01:02:42,680 --> 01:02:44,423
Practice!

701
01:02:44,473 --> 01:02:46,347
Repeat after me.

702
01:02:46,391 --> 01:02:48,550
Collignon, down the john.

703
01:02:50,562 --> 01:02:53,349
- Col... Collignon, down the john.
- That's it.

704
01:02:53,398 --> 01:02:56,104
Your turn now. Go on. Collignon...

705
01:02:59,530 --> 01:03:01,688
Collignon, big moron!

706
01:03:01,740 --> 01:03:04,445
See? You can do it when you want to!

707
01:03:04,493 --> 01:03:07,114
Collignon, dead and gone!

708
01:03:07,162 --> 01:03:09,369
Very good!

709
01:03:09,414 --> 01:03:10,446
Collignon...

710
01:03:10,499 --> 01:03:14,627
- Collignon, big moron, down the john!
- That's it!

711
01:03:22,219 --> 01:03:24,627
OK! That's enough for today.

712
01:03:24,680 --> 01:03:26,673
Enough! Enough!

713
01:03:26,724 --> 01:03:29,678
Lucien, stop!

714
01:03:29,727 --> 01:03:31,470
Very good.

715
01:03:33,063 --> 01:03:36,514
Mr. Dufayel, I found this under your mat.

716
01:04:53,561 --> 01:04:55,600
Still no win!

717
01:04:55,646 --> 01:04:57,722
Me neither.

718
01:05:00,776 --> 01:05:01,807
May I?

719
01:05:03,153 --> 01:05:05,229
There's a little...

720
